description:
The Lamborghini Season is here! Enjoy driving iconic Italian supercars with this limited-time offer. Unlock the Lamborghini Asterion and Lamborghini Centenario. The pile of Credits and Tokens included will also help you to upgrade cars and progress faster.
This pack contains:
40 Blueprints to unlock the Lamborghini Asterion
40 Blueprints to unlock the Lamborghini Centenario
500 Tokens
200,000 Credits
name: Asphalt 9: Legends Lamborghini Pack
